		Method 						     	|  	 				 Purpose
showOpenDialog(Component parent) 			| Opens a dialog to select a file or directory to open. Returns an integer indicating the user's choice.
showSaveDialog(Component parent) 			| Opens a dialog to choose where and under what name to save a file. Returns an integer indicating the user's choice.
setFileSelectionMode(int mode)   			| Sets the file selection mode: FILES_ONLY, DIRECTORIES_ONLY, or FILES_AND_DIRECTORIES.
setFileFilter(FileFilter filter)			| Sets the current file filter to restrict the types of files displayed.
setSelectedFile(File file)       			| Sets the default file name in the Save dialog.
getSelectedFile()                			| Returns the file or directory selected by the user.
setMultiSelectionEnabled(boolean b)			| Enables or disables multiple file selection.
isMultiSelectionEnabled() 					| Returns true if multiple file selection is enabled.
setFileHidingEnabled(boolean b) 			| Enables or disables hiding of hidden files.
isFileHidingEnabled() 						| Returns true if hidden files are not shown.
setAcceptAllFileFilterUsed(boolean b) 		| Determines whether the "All Files" filter is used.
isAcceptAllFileFilterUsed() 		  		| Returns true if the "All Files" filter is used.
addChoosableFileFilter(FileFilter filter) 	|Adds a filter to the list of user choosable file filters.
removeChoosableFileFilter(FileFilter filter)|Removes a filter from the list of user choosable file filters.
resetChoosableFileFilters() 				| Resets the choosable file filter list to its starting state.
setDialogTitle(String title) 				| Sets the title of the dialog window.
getDialogTitle()							| Returns the title of the dialog window.
setApproveButtonText(String text) 			| Sets the text of the approve button (e.g., "Open" or "Save").
getApproveButtonText() 						| Returns the text of the approve button.
setApproveButtonToolTipText(String text)	| Sets the tooltip text for the approve button.
getApproveButtonToolTipText() 				| Returns the tooltip text for the approve button.
setApproveButtonMnemonic(int mnemonic) 		| Sets the mnemonic (keyboard shortcut) for the approve button.
getApproveButtonMnemonic() 					| Returns the mnemonic for the approve button.
setFileSystemView(FileSystemView fsv) 		| Sets the file system view used by the file chooser.
getFileSystemView() 						| Returns the file system view used by the file chooser.